{"tid":829190,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"超越史高斯　拉莫斯成歐聯第一茅柴😄","createTime":"2018-09-20T08:49:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-20T12:55:01.000Z","uid":124667,"like":57,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"c6fda1331fbf79933afde4c1a54526a6ab2e8b93","tid":829190,"uid":124667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T08:49:02.000Z","msg":"皇家馬德里後衛沙治奧拉莫斯周三晚在球隊3:0擊敗羅馬的歐聯G組首輪分組賽，領取自己職業生涯於歐聯的第37面黃牌，令他超越了曼聯名宿史高斯，成為歐聯「第一茅柴」。<br />\n<br />\n今仗是現年32歲的沙治奧拉莫斯生涯第115場歐聯，他在上半場23分鐘於己隊半場飛剷羅馬中場尼桑斯，因而被球證出示黃牌警告。沙治奧拉莫斯現時不單以37面黃牌成為歐聯賽事史上的「第一茅柴」，他亦是單季歐聯領黃牌最多的紀錄保持者，分別在2010/11及2012/13球季領取五面黃牌。曼聯中場史高斯過往在單季歐聯中，從未試過領取多於四面黃牌。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"598d2cde2acaf665b6b33d49ec11754e20527847","tid":829190,"uid":205079,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T08:50:07.000Z","msg":"辣殺"},{"pid":"8f606d315583bed50fc9f4795fd0cfb7283f6c3c","tid":829190,"uid":74272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T08:50:39.000Z","msg":"正路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55f3804c39b493e30cc30e71f104586ff5a244d0","tid":829190,"uid":124667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T08:55:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"159dbb99202a6cb211e06ceb870c1e86484ca34a","tid":829190,"uid":19126,"like":73,"dislike":0,"score":73,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T08:58:43.000Z","msg":"人地踢到40歲先有呢個紀錄，你32就有，真係英雄出少年<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b0fbb882a2e924c69ddc4eb23b73bb5099672c9","tid":829190,"uid":52087,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T08:59:20.000Z","msg":"食牌界世一"},{"pid":"fd388ca27a67c882f62461c07dc9cd25f56d252d","tid":829190,"uid":1823,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T09:00:10.000Z","msg"